(Arizona, California, New 
<collectingCountry id="0B8637B1FFF9FFFAFC5B245FDE26FAFA" box="[969,1064,1364,1390]" name="Mexico" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Mexico</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="3B8B24AAFFF9FFFAFEAA2470D95FFA2A" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="732E7721FFF9FFFAFEAA2470D95FFA2A" blockId="46.[264,1324,284,1470]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis id="41E5AB33FFF9FFFAFEAA2470DBB3FA01" bold="true" box="[312,445,1403,1429]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Etymology</emphasis>
. Named for Reginald Henry Painter (
<date id="072F51E1FFF9FFFAFCE42477D9F3FA02" box="[886,1021,1404,1430]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" value="1901" valueMax="1968">
<number id="C5596506FFF9FFFAFCE42477D9F3FA02" box="[886,1021,1404,1430]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" value="1934.5" valueMax="1968.0" valueMin="1901.0">1901–1968</number>
</date>
) in honor of his contributions to the knowledge of North American 
<taxonomicName id="B4910CA2FFF9FFFAFC9224AFD944FA29" box="[768,842,1444,1469]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Geron" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="41E5AB33FFF9FFFAFC9224AFD944FA29" box="[768,842,1444,1469]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Geron</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
